      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlanta"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The Martin Luther King Jr. National Historical Park preserves the civil‑rights leader’s childhood home and the historic Ebenezer Baptist Church.",
